Installed necessary softwares for VS code to run scripts.
Enabled python and solidity formatting
("pip install black") command is used to install python formatter named black in terminal
to run python program on terminal : python filename (eg python deploy.py)

To compile the solidity code in deploy.py = pip install py-solc-x

Importing compiler: from solcx import compile_standard, install_solc

to install solidity compiler version: install_solc("0.6.0")
